(112, 1, '2024-01-22 03:33:41', '2024-01-22 03:33:41', 'Transport owner says:-Our The higher transport costs are said to have raised the prices of essential commodities, adding to the woes of the consumers who have been struggling because of higher inflation for the past 18 months.Truck, covered van and lorry owners have increased the fare by 20-40 percent due to the blockade since most vehicles have stayed off the roads fearing violence. As a result, traders say, they have had to pay extra to move goods.', 'Ahsanullah Foysal', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '82-autosave-v1', '', '', '2024-01-22 03:33:41', '2024-01-22 03:33:41', '', 82, 'http://localhost/December/WordPresss/wordpress/?p=112', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(113, 1, '2024-01-13 06:29:02', '2024-01-13 06:29:02', '<div class=\"img-box\"><img src=\"images/s1.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-box\">\r\n<div class=\"redesign_synopsis parbase section\">\r\n<div class=\"lp__synopsis\">\r\n<div class=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"lp__synopsis_content\">\r\n<div class=\"lp__synopsis_text\">Air transport is an important enabler to achieving economic growth and development. Air transport facilitates integration into the global economy and provides vital connectivity on a national, regional, and international scale. It helps generate trade, promote tourism, and create employment opportunities. The World Bank has financed aviation-related projects for over sixty years. Today, the WBG remains actively engaged in every region on projects related to air transport policy and regulation, safety, infrastructure rehabilitation, institutional strengthening, and capacity building.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'AIR TRANSPORT', 'Air transport is an important enabler to achieving economic growth and development. Air transport facilitates integration into the global economy and provides vital connectivity on a national,', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'air-transport', '', '', '2024-01-22 04:43:58', '2024-01-22 04:43:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/December/WordPresss/wordpress/?p=113', 0, 'post', '', 0),
