(119, 1, '2024-01-13 06:32:09', '2024-01-13 06:32:09', '<p align=\"left\">We provide 4WD shuttle bus transport to tramping tracks in the Kahurangi National Park, Nelson Lakes National Park, Abel Tasman National Park, The Pelorus, Richmond Ranges, the West Coast and other parks and tramping tracks in the top half of South Island of New Zealand. In some remote areas access may depend upon weather.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Our aim is to provide reliable bus services for all trampers, individuals and groups. We have shuttle vans of average 10 - 16 seats and two buses with up to 33 seats.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">We also provide additional services such as car relocation, mountain bike transport, camping gas, clothes/bag storage, bag relocation and additional stops on request at booking.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Email Trek Express now for availability, bookings, or just a quote.</p>', 'TRUCKS TRANSPORT', 'We provide 4WD shuttle bus transport to tramping tracks in the Kahurangi National Park, Nelson Lakes National Park, Abel Tasman National Park, The Pelorus, Richmond Ranges, the West Coast and other parks and tramping', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'trucks-transport', '', '', '2024-01-22 04:40:42', '2024-01-22 04:40:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost/December/WordPresss/wordpress/?p=119', 0, 'post', '', 0),
